    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The appreciative sensibility of observers who experience delight when disinterestedly observing or experiencing  certain natural and manmade objects and events.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
